title: Ebro In The Morning - Talking Smack: Conspiracy Theories
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 3/29/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Will Smith Slap, some think it's a conspiracy, others do not. Callers tell stories of defending their significant others' honor. 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
